# Privacy Policy — श्रद्धाAI (ShraddhaAI)

**Last updated: April 2026**

ShraddhaAI (श्रद्धाAI) is an offline-first Hindu spiritual companion app. Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how we handle your data.

---

## 1. Information We Collect

ShraddhaAI stores the following information **locally on your device only**:

- Profile name and spiritual name
- Profile photo (selected by you from your gallery)
- Ishta Devata (personal deity) preference
- Daily spiritual goals
- Puja (worship) session records
- Japa / Mala count sessions
- Aarti and Chalisa completion logs
- Custom mantras and aartis created by you
- Vrat (fasting) preferences and logs
- App settings and theme preferences

**We do not collect, transmit, or have access to any of this data.**

---

## 2. Data Storage

All your data is stored **locally on your device** using an SQLite database (via the Drift ORM). We do not:

- Upload your data to any server
- Sync your data to the cloud
- Transmit your data over the internet

Your spiritual practice remains completely private. If you uninstall the app, all locally stored data is deleted from your device.

---

## 3. No Third-Party Sharing

We do not share, sell, rent, or transmit your personal information to any third parties. No advertising, profiling, or user-tracking services are used in this app.

---

## 4. Analytics

The app uses **Firebase Analytics** (by Google) to collect anonymous, aggregated usage data — for example, which screens are viewed. This data:

- Contains **no personally identifiable information (PII)**
- Cannot be traced back to any individual user
- Is used solely to improve the app experience

You can review Google's privacy practices at [https://policies.google.com/privacy](https://policies.google.com/privacy).

---

## 5. Permissions

The app may request the following device permission:

| Permission | Purpose |
|---|---|
| **Photo Library** | To let you set a profile picture from your gallery |

No other device permissions (camera, microphone, location, contacts, etc.) are requested or required.

---

## 6. Children's Privacy

ShraddhaAI is suitable for all ages. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. All data remains on-device and is never transmitted externally.

---

## 7. Data Security

Since all data is stored locally on your device, the security of your data depends on your device's own security (screen lock, encryption, etc.). We recommend keeping your device updated and secured.

You can export or delete your data at any time via **Settings → Backup & Restore**.

---

## 8. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected in the app update notes and on this page. The "Last updated" date at the top of this document will be revised accordingly.

Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.

---

